THE PROGRAM NEEDS INPUT OF TRAINING DATA WITH THE FORMAT AS GIVEN IN "train" file.
THE PROGRAM NEEDS INPUT OF TEST DATA WITH THE SAME FORMAT TO CALCULATE THE PRESISION AND THE RECALL VALUES .
BOTH THE INPUTS ARE GIVEN AS COMMAND LINE ARGUEMENTS TO THE PYTHON PROGRAM.
THE PROGRAM NEEDS THE INPUT FILE "stop.txt" TO BE PRESENT IN THE CURRENT FOLDER WICH CONTAINS THE STOP WORDS.
